<h2 id="additional-notes">Additional Notes</h2>
<ul>
<li>While some people don’t care about uv being fast, it’s shaved minutes off CI builds and container rebuilds —
saving money and energy.</li>
<li>Astral capitalized on a very promising project called
<a rel="noopener external" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/astral-sh/python-build-standalone">python-build-standalone</a> and now maintains it.
These are Python builds that work without installers.</li>
</ul>

        
